ChangeLog
=========

0.3.1 (unreleased)
------------------

*Bugfix:*

    - Fix calling ``setup()`` without providing a loop


0.3.0 (2024-02-02)
------------------

*New:*

    - Add support for Python 3.8+
    - Drop support for Python <3.7

.. _v0.2.0:

